## Gradient System

### Hero Gradients
```css
/* Medical Authority Gradient */
.gradient-medical-authority {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
    theme('colors.soi.navy.800') 0%, 
    theme('colors.soi.purple.500') 50%, 
    theme('colors.soi.navy.700') 100%);
}

/* Care & Wellness Gradient */
.gradient-care-wellness {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
    theme('colors.soi.pink.100') 0%, 
    theme('colors.soi.mint.100') 100%);
}

/* Expertise Gradient */
.gradient-expertise {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
    theme('colors.soi.purple.500') 0%, 
    theme('colors.soi.navy.800') 100%);
}
```

